      <title>研究发现，反 LGBTQ 法律使乌干达损失 16 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-10/anti-lgbtq-laws-cost-uganda-1-6-billion-study-finds-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究发现，乌干达的反 LGBTQ 法律（包括在某些情况下判处死刑）自去年 5 月推出以来，已给该国造成高达 16 亿美元的损失。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-10/anti-lgbtq-laws-cost-uganda-1-6-billion-study-finds-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:44:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
