      <title>1490亿美元资金外流后中国加强对理财产品的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/china-steps-up-checks-of-wealth-management-products-after-149-billion-outflow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，在投资者为追逐股市上涨而撤出约 1,490 亿美元资金后，中国已要求金融机构加强对国内理财产品的监控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/china-steps-up-checks-of-wealth-management-products-after-149-billion-outflow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>优衣库所有者盈利超出预期，预计 2025 财年销售额将进一步增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uniqlo-owner-s-earnings-beat-eyes-bigger-sales-in-fiscal-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迅销株式会社 (Fast Retailing Co.) 通过向新市场的扩张抵消了中国市场经济放缓的影响，因此计划在 2025 财年实现更高的销售额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uniqlo-owner-s-earnings-beat-eyes-bigger-sales-in-fiscal-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国股市价值排名落后于加拿大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/lagging-uk-stock-market-falling-behind-canada-in-value-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国股市在上市公司价值方面落后于加拿大，这对伦敦蜿蜒曲折的股票市场又一次造成打击，近年来，伦敦股市已被印度等新兴交易所所取代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/lagging-uk-stock-market-falling-behind-canada-in-value-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:05:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者准备应对 CPI 风险，卖出日元成为“最热门交易”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/sell-yen-is-most-popular-trade-as-investors-brace-for-cpi-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者为可能扰乱金融市场的美国月度通胀数据做准备，“抛售日本货币”正成为越来越流行的口号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/sell-yen-is-most-popular-trade-as-investors-brace-for-cpi-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
